name: Custom Zelda Theme Triforce Necklace
description: This is a made to order Zelda Triforce themed pendant and chain. Each item is made to order so allow a few days for shipping. Please enquire about international shipping.

name: Rebel Jouel Collar Worn Deconstructed Bow Tie
description:
A unique piece featuring double tiered chain with angular elements hanging in place of a neck tie. Worn under a collar but can be worn without also.

Features extender chain to adjust for different collar sizes.

We make custom items so if you want something made get in touch and we will make it as special order.

If you are local and want to pick up an item from Liverpool then choose 'Everywhere else' for postage so it doesn't charge for it.

name: Personalised Heart or Bone Shape Gold Mirror Engraved Charm, Pet Tag, Pendant or Charm with Clasp
description:
These are made to order custom engraved pet tags or jewellery name charms. Ideal for pet collars, even worn clipped on to existing jewellery chains like in the photo and works as a keyring. We can engrave with any word (within reason depending on length of the name but we can shrink to fit).

They are made of laser cut gold mirror acrylic and come with a golden clasp and jump ring to attach to a pet collar or necklace/bracelet/keys.

We have two shapes to chose from below the heart or bone. Both are between 3-4cm. Once ordered email us with the details of the custom etch you would like.

We make custom items so if you want something made get in touch and we will make it as special order.

If you are local and want to pick up an item from Liverpool then choose 'Everywhere else' for postage so it doesn't charge for it.

name: Designer Neon Letter Door Signs Male & Female
description:
These stylish plaques come in neon as standard with 4mm screw holes but can be ordered in any colour (stock depending, have neon red too) with or without holes (if you use double sided tacks or glue for example). Choose options below to tell us if you want them customised at no extra cost. Once ordered email us with the details of the custom colours you would like.

They feature a stylised M & F letters which are striking to the eye. Our neon glows under a black light too so ideal for dark club and bar toilet doors but equally suited to the home.

If you are local and want to pick up an item from Liverpool then choose 'Everywhere else' for postage so it doesn't charge for it.
